description: This common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 37, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 111, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 5 for North, 8 for East, 2 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [111 Votes, Common]
